@startuml SafeBreach-Labs_hAFL2

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<Host>> LightBlue
  BackgroundColor<<VM>> LightGreen
  BackgroundColor<<Driver>> LightYellow
  BackgroundColor<<Tool>> LightGray
}

package "Linux Host" <<Host>> {
  [QEMU/KVM] as QEMU
  [kAFL Fuzzer] as Fuzzer
  [kafl_gui.py] as GUI
  [kafl_fuzz.py] as FuzzScript
  [Intel PT] as PT
}

package "Root Partition (Windows VM L1)" <<VM>> {
  [Hyper-V] as HyperV
  [VMSwitch] as VMSwitch
  [CrashMonitoringDriver.sys] as CrashDriver
}

package "Child Partition (Windows VM L2)" <<VM>> {
  [Target VSP] as VSP
  [CPHarness.sys] as Harness
}

package "Fuzzing Tools" <<Tool>> {
  [kafl_cov.py] as Coverage
  [kafl_debug.py] as Debug
  [kafl_plot.py] as Plot
}

Fuzzer --> QEMU : Controls
QEMU --> HyperV : Hosts
HyperV --> VSP : Hosts
FuzzScript --> Fuzzer : Launches
GUI --> Fuzzer : Monitors

Fuzzer ..> PT : Uses for coverage
PT ..> HyperV : Monitors

Harness --> VMSwitch : Sends fuzzing inputs
CrashDriver --> Fuzzer : Reports crashes

Fuzzer --> Coverage : Generates
Fuzzer --> Debug : Supports
Fuzzer --> Plot : Visualizes

@enduml